commitResults.messageBody:
DuplicatePersonException extends runtime exception and is never caught.
The check for duplicate persons also happen at other layers. If this exception remains in the codebase and is thrown in the wrong context, the app is likely to have runtime failures.

commitResults.messageBody:
The tests added in this commit checks if the AddOrderCommand reduces
the ingredient quantity in the model if it exists.

This is to prevent int overflow for large quantities.

The overflow will happen if the user puts a large quantity for the
ingredient as well as the order quantity. If the ingredient exists in
the model, then int overflow will occur when finding how much to
subtract.

* Implemented proper storage of Ingredient list
* Fixed bugs related to Price
